text: WJLN (88.7 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of White Springs, Florida. The station is owned by Faith and Action Community Outreach, Inc. It airs a religious format. The station was assigned the WJLN call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on November 19, 2010. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * JLN Category:Radio stations established in 2014 Category:2014 establishments in Florida Category:Religious radio stations in the United States Category:Hamilton County, Florida JLN
